Author: kanaeshiki
Text: Absolutely.. i just feel like I’m suffocating. But yes they definitely know, I’ve expressed I need my space and they’re supportive (lucky to have them).

Author: ISBbaby
Text: Totally get it. If you think it would help, go for it, just let the important people know why.   It can be so tough but being alone in your world can create so much growth.
